        <h2>Nonlinear Collections</h2>
        <p align="justify">
            A Nonlinear collection hold elements that do not have a positional order within the collection. 
            An organizational chart is an example of nonlinear collection.
        </p>
        <p align="justify">
            Nonlinear collections can be either Hierarchical or Grouped collections.
        </p>
